    dc:title "Revision of the Hawaiian endemic leaf-mining moth genus Philodoria Walsingham (Lepidoptera: Gracillariidae): its conservation status, host plants and descriptions of thirteen new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4681863>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4681885>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4681925>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4681927>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4681929>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4681939>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4681977>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4682021>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4682023> ;
